title: Active@ Data Studio 10.1.0.0 Portable
description:
*************************************
Active@ Data Studio 10.1.0.0 Portable
*************************************

Release date: 15/10/2015

Backup & restore your disks, recover deleted documents & photos, erase disks securely, monitor HDD health.

*** This portable version of Active@ Data Studio (83 MB unzipped) includes desktop applications only (run on 32-bit/64-bit systems).

The full (installable) version of Active@ Data Studio 10.1.0.0 (including bootable CD/DVD or USB Disk) is available here https://thepiratebay.se/torrent/12583227

*********************
Applications available
*********************
 	
- Active@ File Recovery 14.5.0.0
- Active@ Partition Recovery 14.0.1.0
- Active@ UNDELETE 10.2.9.0
- Active@ Partition Manager 5.0.15.0
- Active@ Password Changer 6.0.619.0
- Active@ Disk Editor 6.0.37.0
- Active@ Disk Image 7.0.4.0
- Active@ Disk Monitor 3.2.2.0
- Active@ KillDisk 10.0.6.0

*************************
Removed in this portable version
*************************
- Active@ Data Burner
- Active@ ISO Manager 
- Active@ Boot Disk Creator
- Documentation

*********************
System requirements
*********************

- Windows Server 2012 , Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Vista, Windows Server 2008, Windows Server 2003

Homepage: http://lsoft.net/data-studio.aspx
